### Summary

Register a build output path or URI with optional task linkage and content hash.

## How to use

- Required: `project`, `path`. Optional `role`, `task_id`, `content_hash`, `metadata`.

## Project

Pass the same stable `project` string on every tool call for this mount (alphanumeric start; then letters, digits, `.`, `_`, `-`).
